SB 71 Original 2026 Regular Session Boudreaux
Authorizes the commissioner of administration to transfer certain property in Lafayette
Parish to the Lafayette Public Trust Financing Authority. Provides for the reservation of
mineral rights to the state.
Effective upon signature of the governor or lapse of time for gubernatorial action.
